---
// ICP Segment Cards - showing the 5 buyer archetypes with trigger language
---

<section class="icp-section section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="icp-header">
      <h2>We Work With Leaders Who Are Done Patching</h2>
      <p class="icp-intro">
        If any of these sound familiar, you're probably a fit.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="icp-grid">
      <!-- CRO -->
      <div class="icp-card">
        <div class="icp-role">CRO</div>
        <p class="icp-trigger">
          "I can't trust my pipeline numbers. Every forecast is a negotiation, not a report."
        </p>
        <p class="icp-outcome">
          You need systems that give you one version of the truth - so you can defend your forecast to the board without caveats.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- VP Sales -->
      <div class="icp-card">
        <div class="icp-role">VP Sales</div>
        <p class="icp-trigger">
          "My reps spend more time fighting the CRM than selling. The tools are supposed to help us, not slow us down."
        </p>
        <p class="icp-outcome">
          You need a revenue stack designed by someone who's carried a quota - not just built systems for other people to use.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- CFO -->
      <div class="icp-card">
        <div class="icp-role">CFO</div>
        <p class="icp-trigger">
          "We're paying for 7 tools that don't talk to each other. Show me the ROI before I sign another contract."
        </p>
        <p class="icp-outcome">
          You need a partner who guarantees results - $100K+ in recovered pipeline or you don't pay.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- RevOps Director -->
      <div class="icp-card">
        <div class="icp-role">RevOps Director</div>
        <p class="icp-trigger">
          "I know what needs to be fixed, but I'm drowning in tickets and don't have the bandwidth to do it right."
        </p>
        <p class="icp-outcome">
          You need reinforcements who speak your language - allies who extend your capacity, not consultants who create more work.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- PE Operating Partner -->
      <div class="icp-card">
        <div class="icp-role">PE Operating Partner</div>
        <p class="icp-trigger">
          "We just acquired a company with a mess of a CRM. The board wants a clean pipeline report in 90 days."
        </p>
        <p class="icp-outcome">
          You need a team that can start in 2 weeks and deliver a credible board deck - not a 6-month discovery process.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .icp-section {
    background-color: var(--section-dark-bg);
  }

  .icp-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .icp-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .icp-intro {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .icp-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .icp-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1100px) {
    .icp-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }

    /* Make last two cards center on larger screens */
    .icp-card:nth-child(4) {
      grid-column: 1 / 2;
    }

    .icp-card:nth-child(5) {
      grid-column: 2 / 3;
    }
  }

  .icp-card {
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    border: 2px solid var(--border-subtle);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .icp-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--sky-blue, var(--roi-green));
  }

  .icp-role {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--sky-blue, var(--roi-green));
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  .icp-trigger {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    line-height: 1.4;
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .icp-trigger::before {
    content: '"';
  }

  .icp-trigger::after {
    content: '"';
  }

  .icp-outcome {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
